### 2 · Layout anatomy

| Layer             | Key traits                                                                                                                                                                 | Replication tips                                                                                                                                                           |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Global nav**    | 44 px tall translucent bar, blurred backdrop, centre-aligned logo, 11 links, final “bag” icon. Sticks to top on scroll. ([apple.com][1])                                   | Use `backdrop-filter: blur(10px);` plus a semi-opaque `rgba(29,29,31,.72)` background.  Flexbox for equal-width link items; hide labels behind a 24 px glyph below 600 px. |
| **Hero sections** | Full-bleed background (white, black or a product tint), 980-px centred column, product shot above the fold, H1 \~64 px, sub-headline \~28 px, two CTA links.               | Create a `.billboard` component with `padding-block:12rem 10rem` (desktop), `text-align:center`. Swap background colour class by product.                                  |
| **Grid**          | Below the top three billboards the page flips into a **2-up masonry** (two 50-50 columns) showing six product tiles, then reverts to a single-column gallery for services. | Use CSS Grid: `grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr))` and ensure each tile has the same 56 px internal padding.                                         |

