### 4 · Colour & shading

| Token         | Hex (Light mode)            | Usage                                      |
| ------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **Ink**       | `#1d1d1f`                   | All headline & body text on light BGs.     |
| **Paper**     | `#ffffff`                   | Primary hero background.                   |
| **Frost**     | `#f5f5f7`                   | Alt hero backgrounds & section separators. |
| **Link blue** | `#0066cc`                   | Inline CTA links (never buttons).          |
| **Shadow**    | `0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.24)` | Soft drop on product images.               |

Apple swaps to **#fafafa** and **#161617** in Dark Mode; keep tokens in a CSS custom-properties sheet and toggle them via `@media (prefers-color-scheme)`.

