### 6 · Accessibility & performance choices

* Uses system fonts → no font downloads, better CLS.
* High contrast ratios (>7:1 on text over white; >4.5:1 on dark heroes).
* Motion reduces to opacity fades when `prefers-reduced-motion` is set.
* Large hero images (`<picture>` with AVIF/WEBP sources) lazy-load *after* LCP to keep Core Web Vitals green.

